function Start(idActor, flPrevHP, flHp)
	
	Hydra.ActorSetNoDamage(LAKREN_BOSS, true)
	Hydra.ActorEnableAI(LAKREN_BOSS, false)
	Hydra.ActorSetTeam(LAKREN_BOSS, Hydra.TEAM_SCENERY)
	
	Hydra.QActorMoveToLocationDynamicSpeed(LAKREN_BOSS, RITUAL_MARKER, "NPC_Run", true)
	Hydra.QActorSetAnimSetOverride(LAKREN_BOSS, PRAYER_ANIM)
	Hydra.WaitForQEmpty(LAKREN_BOSS)

	Hydra.ActorPlayEffectGroup(RITUAL_MARKER, BURN_BOOK_EFFECT, true)
	Hydra.QActorFadeAndDelete(LAKREN_BOSS, 0.5)
	Hydra.ActorEnable(FALLEN_BOSS)

end

function Start(idActor, idActorDetector)

	Hydra.QActorClearAnimSetOverride(LAKREN_BOSS)
	Hydra.QActorFaceActor(LAKREN_BOSS, idActor)
	Hydra.QActorPlaySimpleConversation(CONV_BOSS_WELCOME, LAKREN_BOSS)
	

end

function Start(idActorNPC, sConversation, idActorPlayer)
